@Module → Class that provides dependencies.

@InstallIn(SingletonComponent::class) → Defines lifetime (Application-wide).

@Provides → Function that tells Hilt how to build a dependency.

@Singleton → Ensures a single instance across the whole app.

@Inject → Constructor/property injection.

@HiltViewModel → Special annotation for ViewModels (works with @Inject constructor).

@AndroidEntryPoint → Marks Activity/Fragment as an injection target.

@HiltAndroidApp → Initializes Hilt at Application level.